         <div id="ctl00_phContent_udpSession">
          <div class="sessionTime" id="ctl00_phContent_sessionTime" style="display:none; padding:10px; font-size:15px;z-index:1000; font-weight:bold; background:red; color:white; position:fixed;left:0;bottom:0;width:100%;">
           <span id="ctl00_phContent_lblSessionTime">
           </span>
           <input class="btnSession" id="ctl00_phContent_btnSession" name="ctl00$phContent$btnSession" onclick="ResetSessionLabel();" type="submit" value="Click here to continue working"/>
          </div>
         </div>
         <script type="text/javascript">
          var sessionTimeout = parseInt("60");
             var _sessionTimer;
             function DisplaySessionTimeout() {
                 //assigning minutes left to session timeout to Label
                 $("#ctl00_phContent_lblSessionTime").html(sessionTimeout);
                 
                 sessionTimeout = sessionTimeout - 1;
 
                 //if session is not less than 0
                 if (sessionTimeout > 0) {
                     if (sessionTimeout <= 5) {
                         $(".sessionTime").show();
                         if (sessionTimeout == 1)
                             $("#ctl00_phContent_lblSessionTime").html("Your session will end in less than a minute.");
                         else
                             $("#ctl00_phContent_lblSessionTime").html("Your session will end in " + sessionTimeout + " minutes.");
                     }
                     else {
                         $(".sessionTime").hide();
                     }
                     _sessionTimer = window.setTimeout("DisplaySessionTimeout()", 60000);
                 }
                 else {
                     $(".sessionTime").show();
                     $("#ctl00_phContent_lblSessionTime").html("Your session has ended.");
                 }
             }
 
             function ResetSessionLabel() {
                 sessionTimeout = parseInt("60");
                 $(".sessionTime").hide();
                 window.clearTimeout(_sessionTimer);
                 _sessionTimer = window.setTimeout("DisplaySessionTimeout()", 60000);// 60000);
             }
         </script>
